71
0:03:24.33,000 --> 0:03:28,000
reasonable space and weight limitations.

72
0:03:28.33,000 --> 0:03:32,000
120 miles is a good enough range for a lot of people.

73
0:03:32.33,000 --> 0:03:34,000
