85
0:04:01.33,000 --> 0:04:03,000
how often would you do it? And it ends up

86
0:04:03.33,000 --> 0:04:07,000
that you'd do swapping less times than you stop at a gas station.

87
0:04:07.33,000 --> 0:04:1,000
As a matter of fact, we added to the contract.

88
0:04:10.33,000 --> 0:04:13,000
