103
0:04:44.33,000 --> 0:04:46,000
as what we call petrol or gasoline.

104
0:04:46.33,000 --> 0:04:5,000
The battery in this sense, is the crude oil.

105
0:04:50.33,000 --> 0:04:53,000
We have a battery bay. It costs the same hundred dollars

106
0:04:53.33,000 --> 0:04:55,000
as the gas tank.

107
0:04:55.33,000 --> 0:04:57,000
But the crude oil is replaced with a battery.

108
0:04:57.33,000 --> 0:04:59,000
Just it doesn't burn. It consumes itself

109
0:04:59.33,000 --> 0:05:01,000
step after step after step.

110
0:05:01.33,000 --> 0:05:03,000
