133
0:06:07.33,000 --> 0:06:1,000
Why? Because batteries life cycle improve --

134
0:06:10.33,000 --> 0:06:13,000
a bit of improvement on energy density, which reduces the price.

135
0:06:13.33,000 --> 0:06:16,000
